00:00:00.250 --> 00:00:02.500
Finally, none of this
can be done legally, or

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:07.590
would be accepted unless EHRs can
ensure privacy so that patient

00:00:07.590 --> 00:00:12.400
data is accessible only to people
to whom the patient grants access.

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:16.570
They must also provide security
from authorized access.

00:00:17.570 --> 00:00:22.730
Other systems for information exchange
must provide a means to establish trust

00:00:22.730 --> 00:00:24.570
to know for sure that the person or

00:00:24.570 --> 00:00:29.430
entities with whom information is being
exchanged are who they claim to be.

00:00:29.430 --> 00:00:32.920
The technologies to help meet
these challenges will be the topic

00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:34.580
of lesson four.

